            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                In <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>onorem</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>omus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ivinae</ex></expan> Minervae san<lb break="no" n="2"/>ct<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> et Genio loci <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Aman<lb break="no" n="3"/>dius Finitus <expan><abbr>opt</abbr><ex>io</ex></expan> princi<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="4"/>et <expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> Celsius Victorinus <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>libr</abbr><ex>arius</ex></expan> principis refecerunt <lb n="6"/>Muciano et Fabiano co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex cert="low">uintius</ex></expan> Catilus <expan><abbr>opt</abbr><ex>io</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>incipis</ex></expan> inchoatum <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>e</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>uo</ex></expan> perfecit <expan><abbr>duob</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>Aug<am>g</am></abbr><ex>ustis</ex></expan> Sev<supplied reason="lost">e</supplied>ro III et <supplied reason="lost">Ant</supplied>onino co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Z. 7/8 wurde ein Jahr später unter die frühere Inschrift gesetzt. Nach der Zeichnung anscheinend von zweiter Hand, kleiner und mit zahlreichen Ligaturen (TIL, PT, AT, VM, IT).</p>
